# CODEOWNERS — required reviewers for protected paths.
#
# How GitHub uses this:
#   - When a PR modifies a path matched here, the listed owner is
#     auto-added as a reviewer.
#   - Branch protection on `main` requires at least one CODEOWNERS review
#     before merge (configured in repo Settings → Branch protection rules).
#
# Format: <path-pattern>   <github-username>...
# Last matching pattern wins, so put broad rules first and narrow overrides
# below.
